    q: "A nurse is caring for a client with gestational diabetes at 36 weeks gestation. The client's most recent hemoglobin A1c is 7.8% and the ultrasound shows an estimated fetal weight at the 95th percentile. Which fetal complication should the nurse monitor for most closely?",
